Na bilo '''iloilo''' e sega ni [[crystalline]], e vakavuqa ni [[mamare]] [[amorphous]] [[kaukauwa]], ka sa rabailevu na kena yaga, ni, kei na decorative, me vaka na kena ivakaraitaki, na [[katubaleka]] pane, [[tableware]], [[optic]], kei na [[optoelectronic|optoelectronics]]. Na kena kilai levu, ka taumada na ulumatua ni iloilo qase duadua, na mataqali bilo manufactured sa ikoya na  "silicate matailoilo " ka yavutaki ena wainimate vakatautauvatataki [[silica]] (Silicon daiokosaiti, se [[quartz]]), na constituent lalai ni [[nuku]].

[[File:Soda-lime glass jar showing bubbles trapped within.jpg|left|thumb|E dua na tavaya ka caka kina na iloilo soda lime. E dina ga ni mamare na iwasewase e sega ni dodonu, na bilo e greenish sobu ena iwasewase vavaku mai na impurities. E tovure na tao tu ena iloilo ni cooled mai na dua na wai, ena veisau ni bilo, ka yaco me dua na ka e sega ni rawa.]]

